The paper deals with the analysis of cache miss cost of algorithms in a parallel environment, taking into account the effects of false sharing. This involves concepts related to distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures (cs.DS), performance analysis (cs.PF), programming languages (cs.PL), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
